<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF108-720-898  </DOCNO><DOCID>08 720 898.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>MacWEEK  August 7 1990 v4 n27 p28(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Coastal Associates Publishing L.P. 1990.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Simplifiler PIM: organizing in fourth dimension. (Zicon SoftwareCorp.'s Simplifier personal information manager) (productannouncement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Webster, John.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Zicon Software Corp. (product introduction).andO;Product:   Simplifiler (Personal information management system) (productintroduction)4th Dimension (Data base management system) (computer programs).andO;Topic:     Product IntroductionPersonal Information Management Systems.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>By John WebsterandM;Lake Oswego, Ore.andP;  -- Zicon Software Corp. recently shipped SimplifilerVersion 1.0, a Macintosh personal information manager (PIM) designed to helpusers organize the stacks of paper strewn across their desks.andM;Created with ACIUS Inc.'s 4th Dimension database, the program, which costs$500, ships with 4D Runtime.andM;The program's 225 preconfigured fields, distributed through eight files, canhold information about business or personal contacts, organizations andproducts.andP;  Users can search and sort files by any keyword, and the softwaregenerates letters using one of four fonts.andM;Although Zicon said the program is geared toward personal management, itsmailing features have made a mark on business users.andM;&quot;We found that it's a valuable sales-management tool.andP;  [The software] helpsus organize mailings to 3,000 to 4,000 agencies per month,&quot; said beta-testerScott Quick of Vision Business Products Inc., a Portland, Ore.-basedoffice-products supplier.andM;Quick said Simplifiler provides macros to speed access to menu commands and atickler file that can be programmed to remind users to send a letter, forinstance, on any date.andM;Users can exchange data between flat-file databases or word processors andthe 4D relational database.andM;Zicon Software Corp. is located at 16580 Maple Circle, Lake Oswego, Ore.andO;97034; (503) 635-9622.andO;</TEXT></DOC>